  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Open up your<strong> wholemeal pittas</strong> (like a book!), then roughly chop into strips</p><p>Peel and cut your<strong> red onion[s] </strong>into quarters, then separate the wedges so you end up with a pile of onion petals</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1654617632719-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1654617632719-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1654617632719-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1654617632719-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1654617632719-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel lengths off your<strong> courgette[s]</strong> with a peeler until you end up with a pile of <strong>courgette ribbons</strong></p><p>Chop the<strong> courgette stem[s] </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1654617636027-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1654617636027-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1654617636027-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1654617636027-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1654617636027-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>onion petals</strong>,<strong> sliced wholemeal pittas</strong> and <strong>chopped courgette stem</strong> to a baking tray with your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>half</strong> the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add a very generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a large pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up, then set aside</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1654617640583-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
