    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> into triangles for per person</p><p>Add your <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> and <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> to a plate and mix them together</p><p>Drizzle a little <strong>olive oil </strong>over the <strong>Greek cheese triangles</strong>, then transfer them to the <strong>mixed sesame seeds</strong> and press down on both sides until they're fully coated – this is your <strong>sesame-crusted Greek cheese</strong></p>",
