    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sesame-crusted Greek cheese</strong> to a separate <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray</p><p>Put both baking trays with the pitta and cheese in the oven for 15-16 min or until the pitta is crispy and the cheese is slightly golden</p>",
