    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze<strong> </strong>the juice of<strong> </strong>half your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into a size bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and the <strong>remaining garlic </strong>(don’t like raw garlic? Go easy!) and stir everything together</p><p>Add the <strong>courgette ribbons</strong> and toss, then set aside – these are your <strong>lemony courgette ribbons</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>tiger tomatoes</strong> into thin wedges and chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 6,
