    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the juice from the <strong>remaining lemon[s]</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>honey</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>honey dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Mix the <strong>salad </strong>through the lemony courgette ribbons until well coated – this is your<strong> lemon courgette salad</strong></p>",
