    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lemony courgette salad</strong> on plates with the <strong>crispy pitta</strong>, <strong>onion petals</strong> and <strong>roasted courgette</strong> over the top</p><p>Add the <strong>tiger tomato wedges</strong> and top with the <strong>sesame-crusted Greek cheese</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>sliced basil </strong>and drizzle over the <strong>honey dressing</strong></p><p>Finish with a grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
